<section id="psycho">
<div class="hidden stagger-1">
<div class="section-label">Section 05</div>
<div class="section-title">Psychoacoustic Effects Lab</div>
<div class="section-sub">How the auditory system interprets spatial cues — from the Haas precedence window to cocktail party attention filtering.</div>
</div>
<div class="hidden stagger-2">
<div class="tabs" style="margin-bottom:1rem">
<button class="btn-active" data-psycho-tab="haas">Haas Effect</button>
<button data-psycho-tab="precedence">Precedence</button>
